1866d8e9d5a4a854db7f5d8c4bc74dbdac1a57418e2d4eab25ef97b96d135a95d30b621b3db8836209d67ece464f692f4074b179bbeaa35633d8717cc47185da  config-postmarketos-qcom-msm8994.aarch64
c2561ffe00687a1fc2ea4a1dec8e132c9c47f522a587cb9d7511a0de9378abe8a5a08428a21822cff8d103c5e61c116182d5adb52e334d69bfc425579bb52f32  0001-arm64-dts-qcom-msm8994-huawei-angler-Add-regulators.patch
"
